com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.snomedrefset

Interface SnomedDescriptionTypeRefSetMember

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.cdo.CDOObject, org.eclipse.emf.cdo.common.id.CDOWithID, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SnomedRefSetMember
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Rf2RefSetMember, SnomedDescriptionTypeRefSetMemberImpl, UnsupportedRf2RefSetMember

    public interface SnomedDescriptionTypeRefSetMember
extends SnomedRefSetMember
    Representation of the description type reference set member. Its purpose is to support description format and maximum allowed length for different description type concepts.

    The following features are supported:

    • Description Format
    • Description Length

    See Also:
    SnomedRefSetPackage.getSnomedDescriptionTypeRefSetMember()
